[normal]. 
[normal]Under 
[normal]“
[normal]detention cases
[normal]”
[normal],
[normal] 
[normal]para
[normal] 5 of Part 1 of Schedule 1 
[normal]of the LASPO Act 
[normal]refers t
[normal]o Mental Health and Mental Capacity cases.
[normal]24
[normal]. 
[normal]We therefore understand that this 
[normal]would still leave the following categories of clients/cases having to meet the residence test:
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]25
[normal]. 
[normal]We stated that we believe that
[normal] this proposal is unlawful, unjust, impractical and unnecessary. It removes access to justice arbitrarily for
[normal] many
[normal] vulnerable client groups and is indefensible.
[normal]26
[normal]. 
[normal]Other responde
[normal]nts
[normal] 
[normal]will cover compliance with Articles 6 and 14 of the E
